	Tie_formatting_problem): add Tie_details to
	Tie_formatting_problem. Update calling conventions.

	* stepmake/aclocal.m4: oops. Include $CONFIGFILE.make, not
	config.make.

	* Documentation/user/lilypond.tely: remove musedata2ly entry.

